613
00:38:50,167 --> 00:38:51,167
Why care that?

614
00:38:54,136 --> 00:38:54,968
Gu Yan is here too.

615
00:38:54,968 --> 00:38:55,808
I run into her

616
00:38:55,808 --> 00:38:56,648
at the store,

617
00:38:56,648 --> 00:38:57,648
