627
00:39:11,768 --> 00:39:12,768
Broadcast hosting.

628
00:39:13,528 --> 00:39:14,648
I'm good at this.

629
00:39:15,367 --> 00:39:16,568
I've also taken that exam.

630
00:39:16,568 --> 00:39:17,728
Maybe I can give her some

631
00:39:17,728 --> 00:39:19,008
